data.description: Location, location, location! Come and see this fantastic family home in Palm Springs. With 4 bedrooms and 2 baths, this property boasts an updated kitchen and bathrooms, complete with a double-wide fridge surrounded by custom cabinets for a spacious pantry. Enjoy the elegance of granite countertops and updated lighting throughout. The bathrooms feature beautiful tile work, and you'll appreciate the convenience of newer AC and a storage shed. Step out onto the patio, which overlooks a sparkling screened-in pool, perfect for beating the summer heat. Don't miss out on this must-see gem!
